  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 400 degrees Fahrenheit",
    "Toss the eggplant, zucchini, red bell pepper, and onion with olive oil, salt, and pepper on a baking sheet",
    "Roast the vegetables in the oven for 30 minutes",
